title: PLAYERS IN NORTH QUEENSLAND.
body: HEY GUYS! i live in North Queensland, and i play alot of league of legends, and i don't really have anyone that i know IRL that plays league. i was hoping to set up some events in North Queensland, and get some of the league community up here to come together and chill  and have a good time maybe once or twice a month. please let me know if your in NQ and want to be apart of this. Add me or leave a comment :"){{item:1038}} {{item:3022}}

replies.body: If you have facebook there is a large QLD group here -https://www.facebook.com/groups/LeagueofLegendsQLD/
